592
00:25:00,630 --> 00:25:01,180
No...

593
00:25:01,270 --> 00:25:02,670
Come in. Come in.

594
00:25:02,790 --> 00:25:03,470
Come in.

595
00:25:04,990 --> 00:25:05,580
Let's go.

596
00:25:05,580 --> 00:25:06,430
Don't go.

597
00:25:07,150 --> 00:25:08,630
