622
00:26:10,870 --> 00:26:11,430
Miss,

623
00:26:11,630 --> 00:26:14,150
how much is the budget of materials

624
00:26:14,150 --> 00:26:14,950
and construction?

625
00:26:15,230 --> 00:26:16,270
To be honest,

626
00:26:18,420 --> 00:26:19,230
