627
00:26:22,270 --> 00:26:24,550
I saw Miss Chen post a recruitment notice yesterday.

628
00:26:24,710 --> 00:26:26,630
I also heard something about your craftsman team.

629
00:26:26,950 --> 00:26:29,420
