658
00:27:34,470 --> 00:27:35,660
It makes sense.

659
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:37,830
You can just tell her that.

660
00:27:38,350 --> 00:27:39,070
I won't object.

661
00:27:39,590 --> 00:27:40,270
Wait.

662
00:27:41,790 --> 00:27:43,070
I think

663
