666
00:27:51,630 --> 00:27:54,630
I want you to tell her not because

667
00:27:54,630 --> 00:27:55,510
I'm worried about Miss Han.

668
00:27:56,670 --> 00:27:59,550
Miss Han, you are not from Lin'an, are you?

